th a fallback.\n\nIf the renderer fails or exceeds its heartbeat budget, then the fallback content is rendered\ninstead.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.withRendererFallback","kind":"def","line":583,"name":"Lean.Doc.withRendererFallback","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L583-L598"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.withMdRendererBudget\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">withMdRendererBudget</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.MarkdownM\">MarkdownM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.MarkdownM\">MarkdownM</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Runs an element renderer with a fresh `mdRendererHeartbeats` budget.\n\nThe budget applies to each renderer separately.\n","docLink":"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.withMdRendererBudget","kind":"def","line":573,"name":"Lean.Doc.withMdRendererBudget","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/DocString/Markdown.lean#L573-L581"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/DocString/Markdown.html#Lean.Doc.mdRendererHeartbeats\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</spa